   Fomichev, Constantin I.; Sokoloff, Dmitry D., Moscow MV Lomonosov State Univ, Biol Fac, Moscow 119234, Russia.
   Briggs, Barbara G., Bot Gardens Trust, Natl Herbarium New South Wales, Mrs Macquaries Rd, Sydney, NSW 2000, Australia.
